1.0.1.name: wordpress/skreverb
1.0.1.description:
This wordpress plugin allows the display of the various ReverbNation widgets on your blog's posts, pages or sidebars, simply and efficiently, by the use of the [reverb] markup.

IMPORTANT: This plugin has been handled over to the ReverbNation team. Please use the new version here
